Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:17.27,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Is she gonna be okay? \NCan she even write a novel?}Ổn không đây? Cậu ta viết tiểu thuyết được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:22.15,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Then again, it's my first time writing, too.}Cơ mà mình cũng lần đầu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:24.67,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{What are we gonna do?}Rồi sẽ ra sao đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:32.46,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{N-Nukumizu! Wh-What are you doing here?}N-Nukumizu? Sao lại ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:34.49,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{What are }{\i1}{you}{\i0}{ doing here?}Còn cậu, Komari?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:36.50,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I-Impolite!}G-Gọi thẳng tên...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:38.62,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{You were impolite first.}Cậu là người gọi trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:41.37,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{But whatever. Adding "-san" is a pain, anyway.}Với cả vậy cho gọn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:43.86,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Are you here to check out light novels, too?}Cậu cũng đến xem tiểu thuyết mới ra à?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:50.34,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\an7\fs14\bord0\shad0\fay-0.035\b1\fscx90\fry12\move(382,184,296,184)\c&HE8EBE0&}{New Comics}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:47.79,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I-I don't know much about them, \Nso I thought I should study some.}T-Tớ không hiểu rõ nên tìm hiểu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:50.34,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{You haven't decided what to write, have you?}Vẫn chưa quyết định sẽ viết gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:54.44,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I've actually already started writing.}Thực ra đã viết từ hồi trước rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:56.14,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Huh? Really?}Thật à?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:59.04,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{M-More importantly, is Y-Yanami...}Q-Quan trọng hơn, Yanami...
