Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.77,0:09:02.55,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Is Yanami joining the lit club, too?}Cậu ấy cũng tham gia CLB à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:05.41,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Sounds like it. Is that a problem?}Có vẻ. Vậy thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:10.53,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Y-Yanami's cute. Yakishio's c-cute, too.}Y-Yanami dễ thương, Yakishio cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:15.95,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Well, you aren't ugly, either, Komari.}Cậu cũng thế còn gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:19.93,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Wh-What?}H-Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:23.16,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I mean...}Thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:35.37,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{P-Pretty girls never join\N the l-literature club.}G-Gái xinh sẽ không bao giờ tham gia CLB văn học.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:38.94,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Hold it right there! You need to apologize \Nto all lit club girls everywhere!}Khoan đã! Mau xin lỗi những cô gái\N xinh CLB văn học ngay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:40.89,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Do it! Now!}Mau lên!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.41,0:09:54.09,Default,Kaju,0,0,0,,{Big brother, are you on your way home?}Anh ơi, đang trên đường về hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:57.25,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Yeah. You sure are late today. Shopping?}Ừm, hôm nay em về trễ vậy? Mua sắm à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:59.49,Default,Kaju,0,0,0,,{Yes. We're having curry udon today.}Vâng, hôm nay là udon cà ri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:05.07,Default,Kaju,0,0,0,,{Big brother, I actually won't be home \Nthis weekend. Is that all right?}Cuối tuần này em không ở nhà, anh ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:07.21,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Huh? I don't really care.}Hả? Cũng bình thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:09.86,Default,Kaju,0,0,0,,{You won't get lonely and \Nstart crying or anything?}Anh không thấy buồn quá rồi khóc chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:11.61,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I'll be fine.}Không sao đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:15.57,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I'll be away this weekend, too. I have \Nan overnight training camp for my club.}Với cả tuần này anh cũng phải đi trại huấn luyện.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:18.77,Default,Kaju,0,0,0,,{Huh? Does that mean \Nyou've finally made friends?}Hả? Vậy là anh đã kết bạn được rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:20.35,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Well, they aren't exactly friends.}Ừm... không hẳn là bạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:21.83,Default,Owner,0,0,0,,{Here you go, Kaju-chan.}Kaju-chan, của cháu đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:25.60,Default,Kaju,0,0,0,,{Sir, can I also get some of your finest\N red beans? I'm making red rice to celebrate.}Có thể lấy ít đậu đỏ không ạ? \NCháu muốn làm cơm đậu đỏ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:26.16,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:28.75,Default,Owner,0,0,0,,{Did something good happen?}Có chuyện tốt hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:31.74,Default,Kaju,0,0,0,,{My brother just made his first friends ever!}Anh cháu vừa kết được bạn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:33.79,Default,Owner,0,0,0,,{Oh! That }{\i1}{is}{\i0}{ good news!}Chà chà, đúng là tin tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:37.41,Default,Owner,0,0,0,,{Everyone in the shop owners' association\N was worried about you!}Mọi người trng khu mua sắm cũng lo cho cháu lắm đó.
