Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:56.17,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{You sure did come through, Nukumizu.}Cơ mà em đỉnh đấy, Nukumizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:58.21,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Um, what do you mean?}Ý anh là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:03.62,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{What else? Yanami and Yakishio. I didn't \Nexpect you to bring cute girls like them.}Thì Yanami với Yakishio. \NEm lôi được 2 bạn nữ dễ thương đi cùng còn gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:06.47,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{It's super rare to see our \Nfemale members in swimsuits.}Được thấy thành viên nữ CLB\N mặc đồ tắm là hiếm lắm nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:09.80,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{What about during swim lessons?}Giờ bơi thấy hoài còn gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:14.77,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{What are you saying? School swimsuits and \Npersonal swimsuits are two different things!}Em nói gì vậy? Đồ bơi trong trường \Nvới đi chơi khác nhau hoàn toàn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:19.45,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Listen. They're bound by the rules to \Nwear official school swimsuits in class.}Nghe đây, đồ bơi trường học\N bị ràng buộc bởi các quy tắc.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:23.34,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{But when they wear personal swimsuits,\N it's because they want to.}Nhưng vói đồ bơi cá nhân thì thoải mái.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:25.04,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Do you see the difference?}Thấy sự khác biệt chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:26.99,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Please explain in more detail.}Xin hãy giải thích rõ hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.34,0:11:29.35,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Okay, okay.}Rồi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:34.11,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Normally, girls are too ashamed to \Nexpose their shoulders and thighs.}Bình thường, con gái sẽ xấu hổ khi để lộ da thịt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:40.19,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{But with the beach as an excuse, they willingly \Nwalk around in what is essentially underwear.}Nhưng biển là ngoại lệ, họ sẵn sàng mặc\N những thứ gần như là đồ lót và khoe chúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:43.40,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Basically, you're allowed to stare.}Tức là để được chúng ta ngắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:46.57,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{No, if you }{\i1}{don't}{\i0}{ stare, \Nit could be considered rude!}Không, không ngắm là thất lễ!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:48.27,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Do you see what I mean?}Đã hiểu ý anh chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:51.52,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I see.}Ra là vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:54.98,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{It's the magic of summer, \Nin a manner of speaking.}Phép màu của mùa hè nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:58.12,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{What the heck are you guys talking about?}Hai người nói cái quái gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.12,0:12:02.26,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Oh, a parasol! \NAnd they even have beach chairs.}Có dù và cả ghế luôn à?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:05.07,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Thanks, Nukumizu-kun.}Cảm ơn nhé, Nukumizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:06.20,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{S-Sure.}À ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:08.87,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Yana-chan, do you have sunscreen?}Yana-chan, cậu có kem chống nắng không?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:11.25,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Yeah, I do. Hold on a sec.}Có. Chờ chút.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:14.04,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{I forgot it last time, and it was terrible.}Đợt trước quên bôi nên rát cả người.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:16.80,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Nukumizu, y-you're looking super pervy.}Nukumizu, nhìn biến thái quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:19.92,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{So, Koto, no bikini?}Koto, không mặc bikini à?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:23.25,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Okay, stop talking and let's hit the water.}Đừng có nói nhảm nữa, xuống bơi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:24.89,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Oh, I'm coming, too!}Em đi nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:27.04,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Wait up! I'll come with you!}Tớ đi luôn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:32.86,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Aren't you going in?}Không đi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:34.77,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I-I'm good right here.}T-Tớ ổn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:36.11,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Here I come!}Đến đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:40.64,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{This is your big chance. \NWhy not spend time with the president?}Mãi mới có cơ hội. \NSao không tận dụng nó với hội trưởng?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:46.30,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Th-That's none of your business. \NH-Hurry up and go in yourself, N-Nukumizu.}L-Liên quan gì cậu. Đ-đi ra đó đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:05.58,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Hey, welcome back!}A, về rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:09.98,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{I have returned! It felt so good!\N The ocean sure is nice.}Ừm! Thoải mái quá. Biển cũng đẹp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:09.74,Top,Koto,0,0,0,,{Man, did I let loose!}Chà, mệt quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:11.31,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{You guys thirsty at all?}Mọi người có uống gì không?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:12.79,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Oh, grab me a cola.}Tớ cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:13.87,Top,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Were you reading this whole time?}Cậu đọc nó từ nãy tới giờ à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:14.77,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I'd like some water.}Em uống nước.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:20.73,Top,Koto,0,0,0,,{Whoa. Yakishio-san, do you have a six-pack?}Yakishio, em có múi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:20.73,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I will never forget this day \Nfor the rest of my life.}Mình sẽ không bao giờ quên ngày hôm nay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:25.29,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{The fact that in my youth, I've enjoyed \None day at the beach with girls in swimsuits}Rằng tuổi trẻ, thằng này đã được \Nngắm gái xinh trong bộ đồ tắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:28.87,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{should sustain me for \Nthe rest of my lonely life.}Nó sẽ nuôi dưỡng mình trong quãng đời đơn độc còn lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:30.62,Top,Anna,0,0,0,,{Hey, guys. What should we have for lunch?}Nè, trưa nay ăn gì nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:32.78,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Wanna buy something and eat it here?}Mua gì rồi ăn luôn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:35.11,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{How about yakisoba?}Yakisoba thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:38.38,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Yanami-san, aren't you \Neating yakisoba right now?}Yanami, cậu đang ăn yakisoba đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:42.33,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I took a chance on a place that \Nwasn't busy, and it was a mistake.}Tớ mua ở chỗ vắng vẻ và cái kết quá dở.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:46.29,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{My intuition's telling me that the shop\N way down at the end is the one!}Trực giác mách bảo hãy vào quán ăn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:48.18,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{You're gonna eat another serving?}Vậy là tính ăn thêm nữa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:49.90,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{I'll go buy some, then.}Em đi mua đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:53.15,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Okay, thanks. Nukumizu, go with her.}Cảm ơn nhé, Nukumizu, đi cùng đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:55.02,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Oh, uh, sure.}À vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:07.09,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Hey, Yakishio-san.}Nè Yakishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:07.75,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Hmm?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:10.65,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Did you get home okay from \Nthe restaurant the other day?}Cậu đã ổn lại sau sự việc đó chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:13.98,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Wait, are you worried about me?}Cậu lo cho tớ à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:19.79,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Well, I was just wondering if what I did\N made you even more depressed.}Chỉ là... nhưng việc tớ làm đã khiến cậu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:26.86,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{You know, he can be really dense, \Nexcept when it comes to his girlfriend.}Tên đó lúc nào cũng ngốc cả, \Ntrừ khi liên quan đến bạn gái hắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.64,0:14:33.93,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{I've been hanging with him for years, \Nbut he never saw me as a girl like that.}Tớ đã luôn bên cạnh cậu ta suốt\N và còn chẳng được xem là con gái.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:43.70,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Yakishio-san, I, well...}Yakishio... à thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.99,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Let's just have fun today.}Hôm nay hãy cùng vui vẻ đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:55.27,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{You're right. Thanks.}Phải nhỉ. Cảm ơn cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.25,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{What?}Gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.13,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Okay, we're gonna run!}Chạy thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.67,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Hey! Wait! Hold—}Này! Chờ! Khoan--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:09.71,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Ow, ow, ow.}Đau...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:13.85,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Nuk-kun, are you okay?}Nuk-kun, ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:20.59,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Nuk-kun, what are you doing?}Cậu làm trò gì vậy trời?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:23.77,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Yeah, yeah. It's 'cause you \Ntook off running, Yakishio-san.}Tại cậu tự nhiên bắt chạy chứ ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:29.11,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Sorry about that. But hey, don't \Nbe so formal. Just use my name.}Xin lỗi nhé. Với cả cứ gọi tên là được.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:29.93,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,Nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:38.16,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{What's the matter?}Gì nữa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.11,0:15:43.84,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{You know, sometimes, \Ngirls just want to be spoiled a little.}Thỉnh thoảng con gái muốn được cưng chiều đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.84,0:15:45.61,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Is that how it is?}Thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:49.49,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Yana-chan was right.}Yana-chan nói đúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:51.96,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{You really are like that.}Cậu lúc nào cũng thế nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:57.24,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{This is great!}Ngon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:04.44,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Komari, don't you want any?}Komari, không ăn hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:08.08,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{The p-president is reading my novel.}H-Hội trưởng đang đọc tiểu thuyết của tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:13.24,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{It's interesting. I think you write \Nreally well. And it's a great title.}Thú vị lắm. Anh nghĩ được đó. Tựa đề cũng hay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:15.22,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{D-Do you mean it?}V-Vậy ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:19.60,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{But you could add a subtitle to \Nintroduce the story a little better.}Nhưng em nên thêm ít chú thích vào cho tựa đề.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:22.27,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{H-How would I add a subtitle?}T-Thêm bằng cách nào ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:27.62,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Well, let's see. If the title was\N"The Literature Club Goes to the Beach,"}Xem nào... Nếu thay tựa đề "CLB Văn học đi biển"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:31.84,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{then maybe, "But We Didn't Realize It Was \Nan Enforced Nudist Beach," for example!}Bằng "Nhưng chúng tôi không nhận ra \Nrằng đây là bãi biển khoả thân" thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:36.01,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Or "Is it True You Get More Points \Nthe More You Strip?" for example!}Hoặc là "Cởi càng nhiều càng nhiều điểm"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:39.52,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{And then your view count \Nwill go through the roof—}Như thế thì lượt xem sẽ tăng chóng ma--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:39.52,Top,Koto,0,0,0,,{That's enough out of you, Shintaro!}Đủ rồi, Shintaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:43.44,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{You, too, Koto? It's not like \NI was telling you to strip or any—}Koto, chờ đã! Không phải tớ muốn cậu cởi--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.03,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{I said that's enough.}Đã nói là im.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:47.90,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Hey! Please stop!}Dừng lại!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:51.86,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Hey, are they holding some\Nkind of event over there?}Nè, bên kia có sự kiện gì đó kìa!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.86,0:16:56.26,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Let's check it out! C'mon, Komari-chan, \Nlet's go. You've been sitting all day.}Đi xem thử đi! Nào, Komari-chan,\N đi thôi. Cậu ngồi suốt à.
