Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.86,0:17:00.83,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\fscx90\bord3\fs30\shad0\fax-0.05\frz4.389\c&H673F1E&\3c&HB7C46E&\frx352\fry10\move(337.333,261.333,337.333,311.333)}{Hitani\N}{\fs20}{Sea Park}
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.26,0:16:58.41,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Huh? N-No, I'm fine.}K-Không, tớ ổn...
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.83,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I wonder if they have food stands.}Không biết có quán ăn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:06.73,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Oh, wow. So this is her thing.}Ra là vậy. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:10.33,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Right? Don't you think \NKomari-chan's novel is well-written?}Nhỉ? Em không nghĩ Komari viết tốt sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:11.70,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Yes, I agree.}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:14.97,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{By the way, what sorts \Nof things do you write?}Cơ mà anh viết gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.01,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Me?}Anh á?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:20.06,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Well, there's this one I've had running \Non Lit Icon for about three years now.}Anh có tài khoản trên Lit Icon được 3 năm rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:23.73,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\b1\fs20\fnTimes New Roman\c&H4C4F54&\frz355.4\pos(322.667,100.667)}{The Slave Girl I Picked Up Was \NActually an S-Rank Adventurer, \Nso I Decided to Become a Freeloader}Cô gái nô lệ mà tôi nhặt được thực ra là một nhà thám hiểm hạng S, \Nnên tôi quyết định trở thành kẻ ăn bám
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:23.73,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\an8\blur0.6\b1\fscy90\fscx190\c&HE7EDF1&\p1\frz355\pos(318,155.334)}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100{\p0}
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.06,0:17:23.73,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\an7\blur0.3\b1\fs8\fnTimes New Roman\c&H4C4F54&\pos(232.667,159.333)\frz355.3}{I thought I was dead when I took a tumble down \Nmy apartment staircase and got hit by a kei truck, \Nbut I woke up reincarnated in another world. \NI was no longer in the big city, with its hectic \Nmorning commutes, and was now in a great forest. \NWith no idea which way to go, I wandered through \Nthe forest until I stumbled upon a girl being attacked \Nby a monster. This chance meeting changed the course\N of my life completely.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:23.73,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\b1\fs10\fnTimes New Roman\c&HBE864D&\pos(265.333,266.667)\frz354.1}{Chapter 1}
