Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.52,0:17:23.72,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Hey, I know this one. I mean, I'm reading it!}Em biết cái này, cơ mà đang đọc luôn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:27.09,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Seriously? I've never met one \Nof my readers in the flesh before.}Thật à? Lần đầu anh gặp độc giả đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:32.44,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I had no idea you were }{\i1}{the}{\i0}{ Tarosuke-sensei, \Nwhose stories have amassed over 20,000 points.}Không ngờ anh lại là Tarosuke tiên sinh, \Nngười đã tích luỹ 20.000 điểm trên web.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:34.52,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Are you gonna publish it as a book?}Anh định xuất bản sách sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:36.47,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{It's nowhere near long enough for that.}Nhiêu đây chưa đủ đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:37.74,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:39.40,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Oof.}
