Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:41.03,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Here. Present for you.}Quà đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:43.16,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Huh? Where'd you get all this?}Cậu lấy đâu ra vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:48.06,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Lemon-chan jumped into the beach \Nflag contest and won this as a prize.}Lemon-chan tham gia cuộc thi cướp cờ và thắng giải.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.70,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Y-You were amazing.}C-cậu tuyệt quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:52.70,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Ah, please continue.}Ai chà, khen nữa đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:55.81,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Guys, we should change \Nand head back to the lodge.}Mấy đứa, thay đồ rồi về nhà trọ thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.81,0:17:56.88,Default,all,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:18:00.92,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Wait, Komari-chan, you haven't \Ngone in the water yet, have you?}Komari, cậu vẫn chưa xuống biển nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:02.39,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Oh, uh, well...}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:06.20,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{We'll be right back!}Đi đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:07.44,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Have fun!}Tận hưởng nhé
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:07.44,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Don't go too crazy!}Đừng làm gì nguy hiểm đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:21.53,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\b1\an8\fax0.15\bord0\fs16\shad0\frz349.8\move(140,269,172,269)\c&H161D19&}{Yakisoba}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.81,0:18:21.53,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Koto, does that one look ready?}Koto, đã chín chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.81,0:18:22.56,Top,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Food tastes so much better outside!}Quả nhiên ăn ngoài trời là tuyệt nhất nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:24.54,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{No, it's still way too soon.}Không, vẫn chưa ăn được.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:24.54,Top,Komari,0,0,0,,{I haven't had b-beef in a while.}T-Tớ chưa từng ăn thịt bò đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:25.18,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{You sure?}Thế á?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:27.36,Top,Lemon,0,0,0,,{How was it, Komari-chan? \NDidn't the water feel great?}Thế nào Komari? Nước mát không?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:28.16,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Oh, but this one's done. Here.}A, cái đó chín rồi. Nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:29.25,Top,Komari,0,0,0,,{I-It was salty.}M-Mặn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:29.25,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Thanks.}Cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:31.21,Top,Lemon,0,0,0,,{I know, right? It feels so good!}Cảm giác tuyệt vời nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:34.71,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I knew it. They're all the type...}Không thể nhầm được. Tất cả bọn họ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:39.26,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{to eat it rare without a second thought!}ăn tái mà không suy nghĩ!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:46.14,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{But I can't just stand here \Nwaiting for time to run out.}Nhưng mình không thể chỉ đứng đây chờ thịt chín.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.77,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I'm going to have to eat it raw!}Phải ăn sống!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:55.67,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Nukumizu-kun, we just put those on. \NLet's wait for them to cook a bit.}Nukumizu, mới đặt lên thôi. Chờ xíu đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:58.19,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Y-You're a real glutton, aren't you?}C-Cậu ăn tham ghê nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:19:01.79,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Here. If you're hungry, eat this.}Nếu đói thì ăn của chị nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:04.09,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Oh, thank you very much.}Cảm ơn chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:07.00,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Someone at a nearby spot \Njust shared these with us.}Người gần chỗ chúng ta chia sẻ cho đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:09.91,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{A middle schooler, maybe?\N She was so cute.}Hình như là cấp 2. Dễ thương lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.49,0:19:11.64,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Red rice?}Gạo đỏ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:23.01,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Immobulus! Expulso!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:28.22,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I'll use the last of the coals to raise \Nthis one right. I'll name her Setsuko.}Mình sẽ dùng cục than\N này nướng em nó. Tên là Setsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:30.21,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Don't you like fireworks, Yanami-san?}Cậu không chơi pháo hoa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.61,0:19:32.48,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I wanted dessert first.}Ăn tráng miệng trước đã.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:33.61,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Gonna toast marshmallows?}Nướng kẹo dẻo à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:36.24,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Ta-da! Mixed organ meats!}Xem đây! Nội tạng!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:37.19,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Would ya look at that?}Cái đó à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:40.66,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{What are you a-doin'?}Làm trò gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:42.86,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{What's up?}Gì hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:47.24,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Uh, well, look...}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:51.60,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{These are too big to do alone. \NI'll do them with you.}Cái này to lắm, để tớ làm cùng cho
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:54.96,Top,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, come on. I can handle this much myself.}Thôi nào, cái này tớ làm một mình được.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:57.34,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Look at those two. \NI wish they'd hurry up and get married.}Nhìn họ kìa. Nhanh cưới luôn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.89,0:20:00.56,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, that's pretty.}Đẹp ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:01.98,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Watch out, watch out!}Nhìn nè nhìn nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:03.17,Top,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Hey, be careful!}Này, nguy hiểm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:04.26,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Oh, there's one left. I'll have that.}A, còn miếng thịt, tớ ăn nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.19,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Ah! Setsuko!}Setsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:07.85,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Huh? "Setsuko"?}Hả? Setsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:09.31,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{No, uh, I mean...}À không...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:12.71,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Hey, if you want it, just say so.}Nếu muốn thì nói đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:16.28,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Here. Aah.}Đây, aaa nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.24,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{It's good, right?}Ngon không?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:28.14,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Mm-hmm.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:31.24,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{So how much is that worth?}Thế giá bao nhiêu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:35.61,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Huh? Uh, um... 700?}700 yên?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.03,0:20:37.60,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:40.00,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I'm just teasing.}Đùa tí thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:50.31,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Idiot! Watch out!}Đồ ngốc! Nguy hiểm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:57.60,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Komari-chan, are you hurt at all?}Komari-chan, có bị thương không?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:00.65,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I-I'm okay.}E-Em ổn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:07.48,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{President, your hand...}Tay anh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.48,0:21:11.83,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Don't worry about me. What would've \Nhappened if you'd injured your face?}Đừng lo cho anh. Mặt em mà bị thương thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:14.81,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I-It doesn't really matter \Nif my face gets hurt.}M-Mặt em sao cũng được...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.81,0:21:16.96,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Don't be stupid. Of course it matters.}Đừng có nói thế chứ, đồ ngốc.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:20.41,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Nobody looks at my face or anything, anyway.}Chẳng ai nhìn vào mặt em đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.82,0:21:22.92,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Well, you do, right?}Ít nhất là có em còn gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.48,0:21:28.41,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Do you really want to relive a bad memory \Nevery day when you look in the mirror?}Em muốn nhớ lại kí ức không vui mỗi khi soi gương à?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.03,0:21:30.66,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{I wouldn't want that to happen.}Anh không muốn vậy đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.05,0:21:32.93,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{P-President...}H-Hội trưởng...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:39.74,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{So don't say stuff like that. \NYou gotta take care of yourself. Okay?}Nên là đừng nói thế nữa.\N Quan tâm đến bản thân hơn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:22:00.36,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{President Tamaki...}Hội trưởng Tamaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.99,0:22:03.80,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I like you!}Em thích anh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:05.12,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Here.}Đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.40,0:22:10.56,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,Komari-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.88,0:22:12.85,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{P-President...}H-Hội trưởng...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.44,0:22:17.62,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I-I've always liked you.}Em đã luôn thích anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.62,0:22:21.19,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{You actually pay attention to me.}Anh luôn chú ý đến em.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.19,0:22:22.43,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{It makes me so happy.}Nó khiến em vui.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.43,0:22:26.08,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I like you. So please...}Em thích anh, nên là...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.02,0:22:31.28,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Please go out with me!}Hãy hẹn hò với em.
